snippet.title: Christmas Shopping - Doki Doki Blue Skies Teaser #3 (Sayori's Route)
snippet.description:
Ever experienced the difficulty of having to buy a gift for someone, but not quite knowing what to get? MC and Yuri know your pain.

Each route in Blue Skies has a sub-plot focus on another girl - with Yuri being the sub-plot focus of Sayori's route. We wouldn't want to forget about the other girls as soon as you get into a relationship, would we?

Join the Discord. Chat with the devs and keep updated with mod updates!

Twitter: twitter.com/blueskiesmod
